1
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:47,960
You are the Mountain God.

2
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:49,560
That's right.

3
00:00:50,040 --> 00:00:52,280
I am the omnipotent Mountain God.

4
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:53,600
I didn't expect

5
00:00:54,040 --> 00:00:56,040
that you, a human, are still awake.

6
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:57,160
Let me tell you.

7
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:58,880
My magic is boundless.

8
00:00:58,960 --> 00:00:59,920
How dare you

9
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:01,680
call yourself a god?

10
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:03,280
I am a god.

11
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:05,290
If you have the guts,

12
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:06,720
hit me.

13
00:01:15,039 --> 00:01:16,120
A mere mortal

14
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:18,600
can actually use the power of the netherworld.

15
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:19,730
Who exactly are you?

16
00:01:20,680 --> 00:01:22,140
You don't deserve to know.

17
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:35,320
Destiny.

18
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:38,479
How will it eventually evolve?

19
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,759
Is it an inescapable inevitability,

20
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:45,640
or a predestined ending?

21
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:49,080
Our blood

22
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:51,920
mutated after being tainted by demonic energy.

23
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:54,280
Thus, it became their eternal prison.

24
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,640
And we,

25
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,440
for the same reason,

26
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,360
are indefinitely imprisoned.

27
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:05,080
I was able to come here.

28
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,920
Is it a turning point of fate,

29
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:10,880
or just a trick of destiny?

30
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:18,640
Child.

31
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,640
Live on.

32
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:23,370
Go live a life without oppression,

33
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:24,880
without duty,

34
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,560
without sacrifice.

35
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:29,320
Just live the life you want.

36
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:35,480
Danyu.

37
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,760
My Danyu.

38
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,720
From now on,

39
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,800
your surname is no longer Li.

40
00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:43,640
Your last name is Lu.

41
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:07,960
I hope you don't open that Pandora's box.

42
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:11,040
Don't use your own blood.

43
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:12,800
Don't be trapped

44
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:15,280
by it.

45
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,120
Lu Danyu,

46
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,360
Danyu.

47
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,160
Baishi Island.

48
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:37,400
So that's how she got her name.

49
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:42,920
Source blood.

50
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,280
How could anyone have

51
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:47,480
such pure source blood?

52
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:45,920
Ah, this...

53
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,250
Ah, this, this, this...

54
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:51,040
The big villain in this world is actually a vampire?

55
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:12,320
You...

56
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,000
Are you...

57
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:34,680
Source blood,

58
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:37,120
is the favorite tonic

59
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,120
of Nether demons.

60
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:39,680
Ah!

61
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,680
What you have in you

62
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,680
is the purest source blood.

63
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:48,760
Ha?

64
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,890
No way, Consciousness.

65
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:52,960
Stop sleeping.

66
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:53,920
Come out and explain.

67
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:56,400
What exactly is this Lu Danyu's identity?

68
00:05:58,760 --> 00:05:59,480
Also,

69
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:02,560
I absolutely didn't bite you

70
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,330
because of your beauty.

71
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,480
Hmm?

72
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,720
Your wound is already healed.

73
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,580
Leave quickly.

74
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:11,000
If you don't leave now,

75
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,260
you'll be surrounded.

76
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:18,760
It really healed!

77
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,480
This is too amazing!

78
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,400
So,

79
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:23,240
was he just healing me?

80
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:25,370
Can demons be so kind-hearted?

81
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,000
Demon?

82
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:27,040
Oh right,

83
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,480
this is a world of gods and demons.

84
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,970
Consciousness!

85
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,320
Didn't you say this Lu Danyu

86
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:35,880
was an unimportant nobody with few ties?

87
00:06:35,880 --> 00:06:38,680
How did she get involved in this kind of family drama?

88
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,010
Wait.

89
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:41,400
This is not the time to think about this.

90
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,450
Why is there a bride lying here?

91
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:00,560
Shishi.

92
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:01,840
Shishi.

93
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:02,600
Wake up.

94
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,440
Wake up, Shishi.

95
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,800
Stop sleeping.

96
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,680
You can't lie here anymore.

97
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:13,280
You'll really become a corpse if you stay here.

98
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,280
Shishi.

99
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:42,880
Shishi,

100
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,200
you're awake.

101
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,440
Lu Danyu,

102
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:48,240
did you save me?

103
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:50,480
I just woke you up passing by.

104
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:52,010
I don't know if that counts.

105
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:54,440
You risked your own life to save me.

106
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,520
Sister,

107
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:56,800
you're overthinking it.

108
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,680
I'm not that noble.

109
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,360
Lu Danyu,

110
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:01,760
you're so sweet.

111
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:03,440
Uh...

112
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:06,200
Shishi,

113
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:07,720
Brother Wuzhou and Sister Mu

114
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,040
also need our help over there.

115
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,600
We can't delay too much.

116
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:11,370
Okay.

117
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,900
I'll follow your lead.

118
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:13,730
Let's go.

119
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:23,800
Hand her over.

120
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,640
Hand over the bride.

121
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:27,200
Hand her over.

122
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:27,640
Hand her over.

123
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,770
Don't try anything.

124
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,880
I won't give her to you.
